summary:
- **Remuneration Report Strike**: First strike received as >25% (25.40%) votes against Resolution 3 (Adoption of Remuneration Report).  
- **Failed Resolution**: Shareholder-proposed special resolution (Amendment to Constitution – Item 5A) not carried (8.96% for, 91.04% against).  
- **Conditional Resolution Withdrawn**: Climate Risk Disclosure resolution (Item 5B) not voted on due to failure of prerequisite Resolution 5A.  

*Omitted: Routine director re-elections, non-material voting details.*
